Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.01,0:00:04.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這個世界上
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.17,0:00:10.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人類的命運究竟是否在由看不見的力量或法則來掌控？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.28,0:00:14.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就像神之手嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.39,0:00:17.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是  至少有一點很明確
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.69,0:00:21.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人的自由不受任何意志的支配
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.74,0:01:44.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,衝啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.21,0:01:46.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰先取下將軍的人頭！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.14,0:01:48.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就重重有賞！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.90,0:02:08.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,B-Bazuso！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.66,0:02:10.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是灰色騎士  Bazuso！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.93,0:02:13.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要我站在這裡  你們休想過去！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.07,0:02:16.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們誰還想再嘗嘗我斧頭的滋味？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.27,0:02:20.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他就是那個能一次屠殺30個人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.64,0:02:22.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還能殺死巨熊的Bazuso嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.25,0:02:24.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不許後退
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.65,0:02:26.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,殺了他有重賞！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.42,0:02:29.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他在說什麼鬼話
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.09,0:02:30.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們只是僱傭兵
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.99,0:02:32.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想幹就自己動手嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.23,0:02:42.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他是誰？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.03,0:02:44.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘿  他還是個孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.87,0:02:46.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看他那把劍呀
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.77,0:02:49.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個小毛孩能舉起那麼大的劍嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.04,0:02:51.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他太沒經驗了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.17,0:02:53.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那種劍只是個看頭！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.34,0:02:54.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他會送命的！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.25,0:02:58.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真的想和我斗嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.98,0:03:01.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你倒真有些膽量呢，小鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.92,0:03:04.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  當我用斧子砍掉你的頭時
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.79,0:03:09.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你馬上就會後悔的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.73,0:03:10.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或者應該說是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.96,0:03:14.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像你這樣小小年紀就要被送上戰場還真是可憐
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.53,0:03:17.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來你的軍隊裡還真是人手不足啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.90,0:03:21.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拿個小鬼作掩護  你們其他的人都是膽小鬼嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.04,0:03:27.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好-好快！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.88,0:03:29.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,力量也好大！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.18,0:03:31.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看吶  Bazuso招架不住了！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.48,0:04:00.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等-等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.46,0:04:18.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是現在！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.66,0:04:20.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所有人快衝啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.07,0:04:25.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我還不知道我們的對手中還有這樣厲害的傢伙呀
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.00,0:04:27.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他真的只是個僱傭兵嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.97,0:04:30.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在想他會不會比你還強？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.34,0:04:32.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,傻瓜  和我們的頭根本不在一個檔次
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.74,0:04:34.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對吧  Griffith？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.64,0:04:35.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,撤退吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.98,0:04:36.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.98,0:04:40.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們已經守衛城堡3個月了  早就超過了當初3天的約定
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.82,0:04:42.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且我們已經幫助那個地方領主逃脫了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.89,0:04:45.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,該做的都做了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.37,0:04:59.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是你這次戰鬥的酬勞
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.34,0:05:00.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,點點吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.60,0:05:02.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我必須承認  我非常吃驚
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.11,0:05:06.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為就算你這個新手是偶然打敗Bazuso的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.04,0:05:09.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也太不可思議了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.65,0:05:13.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你可否考慮為我長期工作？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.75,0:05:16.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的酬勞會是現在的3倍
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.25,0:05:18.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我還可以給你一個你想要的封號
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.52,0:05:22.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣的條件對一個僱傭兵來說可是非常豐厚的呀
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.03,0:05:23.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.46,0:05:28.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們的合同今天到期了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.90,0:05:31.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡的戰鬥也結束了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.37,0:05:33.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.94,0:05:36.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會同時保障你的地位和收入的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.24,0:05:39.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也不用再去親自上陣
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.31,0:05:41.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把手拿開！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.34,0:05:42.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.58,0:05:45.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不許再碰我一下！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.21,0:06:12.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.24,0:06:14.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有人來了！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.28,0:06:14.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.91,0:06:18.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘿！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.02,0:06:22.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇  這不是那個擊敗了Bazuso的傢伙嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.25,0:06:23.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他怎麼到這來了？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.12,0:06:25.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他可是敵人  該不該抓住他？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.72,0:06:28.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了吧  我們剛打完仗  對不對？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.46,0:06:33.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是  他的錢袋可是鼓鼓的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.36,0:06:37.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他一定靠打敗Bazuso賺了不少錢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.34,0:06:40.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Griffith  我們能下手嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.14,0:06:46.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隨你們的便
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.14,0:06:49.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的  夥計們  跟我來
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.21,0:06:52.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.65,0:06:54.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什麼可笑的  Caska？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.08,0:06:57.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你贏不了他的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.85,0:06:59.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是你的想法  其實
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.89,0:07:02.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我原本就是打算要靠擊敗Bazuso來出人頭地
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.33,0:07:06.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要是不把破壞我計劃的這個浪人打敗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.40,0:07:08.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是不會善罷甘休的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.00,0:07:09.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你會死的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.64,0:07:14.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那你就好好看著吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.91,0:07:20.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唉  Corkus他們呀
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.61,0:07:22.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Griffith  讓他們這樣做合適嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.86,0:07:38.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我的幻覺嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.53,0:07:44.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,強盜嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.57,0:07:45.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Dan  抓住他！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.00,0:07:46.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.43,0:08:12.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這-這個傢伙太強了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.63,0:08:16.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快看  那傢伙打敗了Dan和Earl！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.17,0:08:17.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,該死！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.53,0:08:19.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們在幹什麼呀？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.27,0:08:22.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Corkus真是自作自受
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.61,0:08:24.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看吧  我就說過
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.54,0:08:25.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Caska
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.71,0:08:28.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你最好幫幫他
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.64,0:08:30.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等-等一下！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.11,0:08:31.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在開玩笑吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.28,0:08:32.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是Corkus的錯！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.58,0:08:35.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧  我去就是了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.99,0:08:41.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗨  Riguel  該你上了！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.09,0:08:43.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為-為什麼是我？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.04,0:08:56.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Caska
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.01,0:08:58.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你-你是來支援我的嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.14,0:09:01.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不是來幫你的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.74,0:09:03.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是Griffith的命令
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.75,0:09:05.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,退後
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.94,0:09:29.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是個女孩！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.27,0:09:32.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這個混蛋！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.48,0:09:42.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  快看
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.65,0:09:44.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Caska被逼到死角了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.72,0:09:47.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有Griffith曾經擊敗過Caska！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.29,0:09:49.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他這劍術
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.19,0:09:50.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有他的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.90,0:09:56.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會死的！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.61,0:10:06.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Griffith！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.94,0:10:08.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Griffith？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.55,0:10:11.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小心點  他很厲害的！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.48,0:10:15.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你可以把劍收起來嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.76,0:10:20.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.10,0:10:33.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.58,0:10:47.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太快了！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.59,0:10:57.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,了不起！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.73,0:10:58.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是一擊就
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.86,0:11:00.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呼  真是個笨蛋呀！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.20,0:11:03.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想單挑Griffith還差得遠呢！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.17,0:11:05.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Corkus！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.30,0:11:07.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這一切都是你的錯誤造成的！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.34,0:11:09.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對-對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.51,0:11:16.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你-你
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.95,0:11:18.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,退後  Caska
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.83,0:11:37.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Griffith！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.68,0:12:56.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Gambino！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.48,0:13:00.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Gambino  幫幫我！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.22,0:13:01.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的劍對這個怪物不起作用！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.45,0:13:06.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Gambino？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.92,0:13:08.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別說傻話了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.56,0:13:11.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難到你忘了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.73,0:13:13.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我早就不生活在這個世界上了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.03,0:13:20.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你用劍刺穿了我的身體
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.74,0:13:21.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓我痛苦的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.34,0:13:24.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.94,0:13:27.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Gambino！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.74,0:13:29.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請聽我說  我當時
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.02,0:13:34.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幫幫我  Gambino！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.35,0:13:37.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是你應得的懲罰
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.12,0:13:39.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你理應受死
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.29,0:13:42.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你理應受死
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.86,0:13:44.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你理應受死
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.19,0:13:47.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你理應受死
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.30,0:13:49.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你理應受死
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.23,0:13:51.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你理應受死
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.27,0:13:52.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你理應受死
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.77,0:13:53.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原諒我！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.90,0:13:55.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Gambino！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.17,0:13:56.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,求求你！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.28,0:14:05.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別碰我
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.45,0:14:07.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要碰我
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.95,0:14:10.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要碰我
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.05,0:14:13.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請不要碰我
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.29,0:14:16.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.26,0:14:23.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是誰？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.00,0:14:26.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,女的？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.67,0:14:30.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黑色的眼睛
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.62,0:14:44.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我這是在哪？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.61,0:15:11.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,僱傭兵的營地？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.41,0:15:13.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們看起來歲數都不大
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.69,0:15:20.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.20,0:15:29.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黑色的眼睛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.17,0:15:38.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.67,0:15:41.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個時候就該被Griffith殺掉了！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.42,0:15:47.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一點也不奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.22,0:15:52.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Caska一直就反感自己作為傭兵生活的現狀
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.92,0:15:56.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她可比我們其他人都要強
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.83,0:15:59.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對她來說，尤其是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.80,0:16:02.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當Griffith兩天前下令讓她躺在你身邊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.13,0:16:04.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為失血過多  身體僵硬的你
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.73,0:16:07.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,溫暖身子時  她就更無法接受了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.07,0:16:11.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他只是說「女人給男人暖身子是理所應當的吧」
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.48,0:16:14.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她把你從床上踢下來嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.45,0:16:18.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我叫Griffith
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.08,0:16:20.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的名字是？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.55,0:16:22.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Guts
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.15,0:16:26.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是把好劍呀
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.99,0:16:28.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可用不了它
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.06,0:16:33.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟我來好嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.04,0:16:46.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼他們的目光
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.18,0:16:48.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看起來都這麼不友善？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.85,0:16:51.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鷹之團
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.75,0:16:52.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鷹之團？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.98,0:16:54.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽說過我們吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.18,0:16:56.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是聽過一些謠傳
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.19,0:16:58.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鷹之團
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.59,0:17:01.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一隻被稱作死神的僱傭兵部隊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.99,0:17:05.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那座城堡就是因為有Hawk的進駐才堅守了3個月
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.26,0:17:07.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,儘管別人都說他們只能守3天
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.63,0:17:12.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,儘管如此  我從沒想過鷹之團的成員都是些孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.47,0:17:19.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Griffith究竟在搞什麼？想施恩於那個廢物嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.61,0:17:22.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想他要那個人加入我們的隊伍
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.35,0:17:25.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們親眼見過他是多麼的厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.15,0:17:28.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我確信他的加入會大大增強我們的戰鬥力
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.69,0:17:32.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別開玩笑了  Ricket！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.69,0:17:37.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他砍掉了Earl的手臂  還殺了Dan！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.56,0:17:40.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個混蛋殺了我們的戰友  我不會坐視不管的！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.53,0:17:42.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不對  Pippin？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.51,0:18:00.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,風景不錯吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.62,0:18:03.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.39,0:18:06.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你那個時候就有機會置我於死地
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.19,0:18:09.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這對你來說很容易呀
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.49,0:18:10.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你為什麼沒有殺死我？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.60,0:18:17.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想讓你做我的士兵
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.13,0:18:19.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Guts
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.04,0:18:25.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在城堡親眼目睹了你和Bazuso的決鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.24,0:18:26.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那真是場精彩的戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.64,0:18:28.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.09,0:18:39.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個時候好險
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.06,0:18:44.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果Bazuso的斧頭沒有斷裂的話
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.23,0:18:48.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你可能已經身首異處了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.80,0:18:50.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也許吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.03,0:18:53.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你倒是很誠實
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.17,0:18:56.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從你的戰鬥方式可以看出
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.44,0:19:00.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你總是在拿生命來冒險
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.45,0:19:05.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不論是面對Bazuso那樣的怪物還是Corkus他們的攻擊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.58,0:19:09.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也毫不懼怕
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.52,0:19:15.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相反  你不顧一切的用劍來挑戰
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.29,0:19:18.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你確實很勇敢  可是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.49,0:19:22.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我相信你這樣冒險的目的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.50,0:19:25.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是想通過戰鬥來尋找生存的意義
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.27,0:19:26.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可以感覺出來
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.84,0:19:32.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真有意思
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.11,0:19:35.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我發現你我很像
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.25,0:19:38.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我希望你能加入我們  Guts！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.56,0:19:50.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.99,0:19:52.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.43,0:19:54.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼要跟我說這些？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.60,0:19:58.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果我說不呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.97,0:20:00.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不想嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.20,0:20:02.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然了  我拒絕！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.74,0:20:11.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別自以為是了！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.48,0:20:13.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你瞭解我有多少？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.68,0:20:17.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們之前從沒見過  你怎麼可能瞭解我？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.42,0:20:18.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我確實不是很瞭解你
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.02,0:20:20.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可我可以感覺到
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.16,0:20:23.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這卑鄙的傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.73,0:20:28.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刺傷了我  又對我假施善心！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.03,0:20:30.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你先挑起的頭！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.00,0:20:33.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是不會忘記這一點的！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.97,0:20:38.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我同樣也不指望你會原諒我殺了你的手下
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.98,0:20:42.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你我可是敵人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.35,0:20:44.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那你想怎麼樣？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.85,0:20:46.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼  很簡單
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.22,0:20:55.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用劍來一決勝負吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.13,0:21:01.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我贏了的話  就要在你身上戳個一樣的洞！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.73,0:21:04.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果我贏了呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.57,0:21:06.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就悉聽尊便！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.07,0:21:09.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.41,0:21:18.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也很喜歡用武力來解決問題
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.61,0:21:19.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Griffith！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.92,0:21:22.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不許插手  Caska
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.72,0:21:23.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但-但是
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.72,0:21:27.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無論如何我都會得到自己想要的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.32,0:21:30.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我受夠了你的傲慢自大
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.66,0:21:33.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真讓我噁心！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.19,0:23:13.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,故事開始了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.00,0:23:17.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們的命運終於連在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.60,0:23:20.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少年的吶喊  少女的思念
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.60,0:23:25.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想要的東西  一定要得到
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.20,0:23:32.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但那只會揮劍的少年   又該何去何從呢？
